{"id":176395,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":1,"day":27}],"page":"5","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"文学界(第8期)","column":"","genre":"","count":"327","ytitle":"","mtitle":"购买公债板话","ftitle":"","authors":["阮清华"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"阮清华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同胞们:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知道吗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年是啥年?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是个经济困难年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为啥经济会困难?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且听我来说端详:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放地区天天扩大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动俘虏要来养他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城乡交通需要恢复，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发展生产那能怠慢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这笔款子那儿去想?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家经济还有困难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说道“我们有困难、有办法、有希望。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办法办法何处去想?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望希望又在那方?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同胞们:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且莫慌!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办法希望都在自家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二亿分胜利折实公债，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切都能迎刃而解。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公债的发行顶公道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有钱的出钱来购买，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无钱的出力去宣传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家全力支持销公债，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家经济就不会困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弥补赤字预算不足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稳定物价不再上涨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通货大部回进笼中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民生活有了保障。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奉劝同胞们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全心全力购买公债，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与国与己都有利益，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一举两得何乐不为?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快来买胜利公债!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快来买胜利公债!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年一月十六日"}]}